<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Account Under Verification</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      body {
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(20,184,166,.08), transparent 28%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #0f172a 0%, #111827 100%);
        color: #e5e7eb;
      }

      .verification-card {
        background: rgba(15,23,42,.92);
        border: 1px solid rgba(148,163,184,.16);
        color: #e2e8f0;
      }

      .verification-card .text-muted {
        color: #94a3b8 !important;
      }

      .verification-card .alert-light {
        background: rgba(30,41,59,.96);
        color: #e2e8f0;
        border-color: rgba(148,163,184,.16);
      }

      .verification-card .alert-warning {
        background: rgba(245,158,11,.14);
        color: #fde68a;
        border-color: rgba(245,158,11,.18);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container vh-100 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
      <div class="card verification-card shadow-sm rounded-4" style="max-width: 580px;">
        <div class="card-body p-4 p-md-5 text-center">
          <div class="small text-uppercase text-muted fw-semibold mb-2" style="letter-spacing: .08em;">Faculty Verification</div>
          <h2 class="fw-bold mb-2">Your faculty profile is waiting for approval</h2>
          <p class="text-muted mb-4">
            Your account was created successfully, but you cannot sign in as faculty until a website administrator verifies your profile.
          </p>

          <div class="alert alert-warning rounded-3 text-start">
            <div class="fw-semibold mb-1">Why this is required</div>
            <div>
              This extra review is a security step so that not anyone can sign up and access faculty-only features.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="alert alert-light border rounded-3 text-start mb-0">
            <div class="fw-semibold mb-1">What to do next</div>
            <div>Please contact the website administrator for verification. Until your profile is verified, you will not be able to log in.</div>
          </div>

          <%= link_to "Back to Login", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-dark btn-lg rounded-3 mt-4" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
